# TeseSharp
A .NET port of text serializer library

## How to use?
```csharp
var adr = new Address { 
	      City = new City {
			 Name = "Berlin", State = State.UT, Code = 12345
		     },
	      Street = "Main Road", Number = 21, Postal = 42
};
			
var tese = new Tese();
using (var writer = File.OpenWrite("test.txt")) {
    tese.Serialize(adr, writer);
}
```

## Example storing
```
# 01.09.2016 21:33:28
.street=Main Road
.number=21
.postal=42
.city.name=Berlin
.city.state=UT
.city.code=12345
```
